1. *Rita* je danas bila u gradu. (Rita was in town today.)
2. Da li si video *Ritu* danas? (Have you seen Rita today?)
3. Ovo je *Ritin* telefon. (This is Rita's phone.)
4. *Riti* je potrebna pomoć oko spremanja hrane za večeru. (Rita needs help with cooking dinner.)
5. *Ritine* oči su plave. (Rita's eyes are blue.)
6. *Ritin* pas je veliki i crn. (Rita's dog is big and black.)
7. *Rita* peva jako lepo. (Rita sings very beautifully.)
8. *Riti* se dopada tvoja nova frizura. (Rita likes your new hairstyle.)
9. *Ritina* majka je veoma ljubazna. (Rita's mother is very kind.)
10. *Ritine* prijateljice su sjajne. (Rita's friends are great.)

(Note: In Serbian, the word "Rita" is written with a Cyrillic alphabet as "Рита". The star symbol (*) is used here to indicate the word "Rita" in each sentence.) 

Translations:
1. Rita je danas bila u gradu. (Rita was in town today.)
2. Have you seen Rita today? (Da li si video Ritu danas?)
3. This is Rita's phone. (Ovo je Ritin telefon.)
4. Rita needs help with cooking dinner. (Riti je potrebna pomoć oko spremanja hrane za večeru.)
5. Rita's eyes are blue. (Ritine oči su plave.)
6. Rita's dog is big and black. (Ritin pas je veliki i crn.)
7. Rita sings very beautifully. (Rita peva jako lepo.)
8. Rita likes your new hairstyle. (Riti se dopada tvoja nova frizura.)
9. Rita's mother is very kind. (Ritina majka je veoma ljubazna.)
10. Rita's friends are great. (Ritine prijateljice su sjajne.)